It's been a while since I've talked about my book in this newsgroup.  For
those of you are paying attention, this is the current table of contents.
The book will be published by John Wiley & Sons this Fall.

	-Bruce


                       APPLIED CRYPTORAPHY
           PROTOCOLS, ALGORITHMS, AND SOURCE CODE IN C
                                         by  Bruce Schneier   

